        <updateDate>2020-10-26T17:34:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> <b>Redeeming Effectiveness to Carbon Oxide Utilization Plus Sequestration Act of 2020 or the RECOUPS Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows taxpayers who claim a carbon oxide sequestration tax credit to elect to treat the credit as a payment in excess of tax liability. This allows the taxpayer a direct payment of 90% of the dollar amount of the credit.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
